data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF and 6in GUTTERS installed 9/28/23 waiting to put the warranty in your name! Come check out this well-maintained one-story home in the Greystone subdivision! This split floorplan features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. High ceilings in the entry and dining room allow tall windows that let in an abundance of natural light. The open living/dining/kitchen concept is great for entertaining or just keeping an eye on everyone. The primary features tray ceilings, a dual vanity, walk-in closet, separate shower and jetted garden tub. The large covered back patio and mature trees provide some relief from the Texas heat. Separate laundry room leads to the clean two car garage. Window blinds and all new carpet throughout the house. And the best part of all...NO HOA!!!
